                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4" style="border-radius: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #0d6efd;">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3"><i class="fas fa-book-open me-2"></i>What is CRISP-DM?</h4>
                    <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                        CRISP-DM is a clear guide that helps data scientists manage their projects from start to finish. It acts as a standard map for data mining projects.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4" style="border-radius: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #fd7e14;">
