                    <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                        Created in 1996 by experts from DaimlerChrysler and SPSS to build a simple process that works for any type of industry.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 mb-5 text-center" style="border-radius: 15px;">
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-muted">The Lifecycle Diagram</h5>
