        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">The 6 Phases of CRISP-DM</h2>
            <p class="text-muted small">Click on any card below to view detailed Activities & Outputs</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-primary mb-2"><i class="fas fa-briefcase fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">1. Business Understanding</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Defining project goals and business requirements.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-primary small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Set clear goals and plan the timeline for the project.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A basic plan on how to achieve the business goals.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-info mb-2"><i class="fas fa-search fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">2. Data Understanding</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Collecting and exploring the data for initial insights.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-info small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Explore the data (EDA) and check for any quality issues.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A report explaining the quality and types of data collected.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-secondary mb-2"><i class="fas fa-tools fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">3. Data Preparation</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Cleaning and formatting the data for analysis.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-secondary small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Fix missing values and merge different data sources together.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A clean and final dataset ready for modeling.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-warning mb-2"><i class="fas fa-brain fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">4. Modeling</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Building and testing mathematical models on the data.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-warning small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Select the best model and test it using the prepared data.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A prediction model that can find patterns in data.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-danger mb-2"><i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">5. Evaluation</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Reviewing if the model meets the business objectives.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-danger small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Compare the model results against the initial business goals.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A final decision on whether to launch the project or not.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4 phase-card">
                    <div class="text-center mb-3">
                        <div class="d-inline-block p-3 rounded-circle bg-light text-success mb-2"><i class="fas fa-rocket fa-2x"></i></div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">6. Deployment</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted text-center mb-0">Implementing final results for everyday business use.</p>
                    <div class="text-center mt-2 text-success small fw-bold">View Activities & Output <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1"></i></div>
                    <div class="phase-details small text-secondary">
                        <ul class="ps-3 mb-0 text-start">
                            <li class="mb-2"><strong>What we do:</strong> Create a user-friendly dashboard and plan for system maintenance.</li>
                            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> A working system or report that others can use daily.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4" style="border-top: 5px solid #198754; border-radius: 15px;">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold"><i class="fas fa-thumbs-up text-success me-2"></i>Advantages </h5>
                    <ul class="text-secondary small mt-3">
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Flexible:</strong> It can go back and forth between stages to refine it work.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Business Centered:</strong> It ensures that the project actually solves a real problem.</li>
                        <li><strong>Standardized:</strong> It provides a clear blueprint that any industry can understand.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100 p-4" style="border-top: 5px solid #dc3545; border-radius: 15px;">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold"><i class="fas fa-thumbs-down text-danger me-2"></i>Possible Challenges</h5>
                    <ul class="text-secondary small mt-3">
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Documentation:</strong> Recording every detail can be quite time-consuming.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Project Speed:</strong> It might feel slow for teams that need instant results.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

